  "description": {
    "en": "One space-side face of a wall: the per-room view of a shared wall. Created by the BIM import per (space, wall) pair — external id is the composite of the space and wall Revit GUIDs; the inherited geometryExternalID carries the bounding wall's Revit GUID for viewer selection. The import owns the geometry contribution (name, area); condition and makeup fields are manual Syyclops entries that survive re-imports. Related to its Space via the inherited locatedIn and to its Wall via faceOf."
  }
